Contains classes for parametric fitting of 1-dimensional histograms.
jam.global - package jam.global
Classes containing application status information and useful methods that any class in Jam may use.
jam.io - package jam.io
Contains classes for storing histograms and/or gates and scalers to files.
jam.io.hdf - package jam.io.hdf
Pure Java implementation to store histograms, gates, and scalers in the HDF 4.1 format.

Classes for controlling the representation of the plots portion of Jam's display.
jam.sort - package jam.sort
Classes for controlling the retrieval, sorting and storage of data, including the user-extensible jam.sort.SortRoutine.

Customizable classes defining the data format to be sorted.

A few useful classes for performing some common tasks, such as opening file dialogs, formatting numbers and String manipulation.
